==Description==
The '''Yellow Shard''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The Yellow Shard can be used, alongside [[Quest Points]] {{Questpoints}}, to purchase items at the [[Shard Trader|Shard Traders]].

==Mine Layout==
The Yellow Shard appears in the Underground as a 4x3 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:YellowShardMine.png|100px]]

==Trades==
Yellow Shards can be used to purchase the following items:
